crs = {'init':'epsg:4326'}
geometry = [Point(x,y) for x,y in zip(df['Longitude'], df['Latitude'])]
geo_df = gpd.GeoDataFrame(df, crs = crs, geometry = geometry).to_crs(epsg=4326)
